code: @Test public void testAtomHttpNoCamelParameters() throws Exception {     AtomEndpoint atom = context.getEndpoint("atom://http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?sortEntries=true&feedHeader=true", AtomEndpoint.class).     assertNotNull(atom).     assertEquals("http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml", atom.getFeedUri()).     assertEquals(true, atom.isFeedHeader()).     assertEquals(true, atom.isSortEntries()). }

@Test public void testAtomHttpNoCamelParametersAndOneFeedParameter() throws Exception {     AtomEndpoint atom = context.getEndpoint("atom://http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?sortEntries=true&feedHeader=true&foo=bar", AtomEndpoint.class).     assertNotNull(atom).     assertEquals("http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?foo=bar", atom.getFeedUri()).     assertEquals(true, atom.isFeedHeader()).     assertEquals(true, atom.isSortEntries()). }
